Subject: [PATCH 5.4 044/168] drm/amd/display: Not doing optimize bandwidth if flip pending.
Date:   Tue, 28 Apr 2020 20:23:38 +0200
Message-Id: <20200428182237.448944669@linuxfoundation.org>
